description:
🩸a game made in 2 hours

👁This ended up being kind of a fidget toy game where you spin your cursor around fast to avoid a tear drop.  

ℹ️This was a 1 hour challenge, I made all the art, sounds and majority of the code in an hour(and then extra time to fix the highscore system and tweak the speed of the tear!)
